					"type": 23,
					"value": "Lens the Journalist is near the checkpoint at the South Checkpoint. She is taking notes and observing intently to the happenings around her.\r\n\r\nThis is the AD that's been repeated as she stands there. Orin will also use this AD when she impersonates Lens."
